  "steps": [
    {
      "order": 1,
      "instruction": "If you are using whole prawns, remove heads and peel them. Leave a few whole for decorative purposes, if you wish. I find that with medium size already cooked prawns, deveining is usually not necessary (it's hard to do + so small it's barely noticeably especially with sauce)."
    },
    {
      "order": 2,
      "instruction": "Mix together Sauce in a small bowl."
    },
    {
      "order": 3,
      "instruction": "Toss prawns with Sauce."
    },
    {
      "order": 4,
      "instruction": "Place a bit of lettuce in serving dishes. I like to use Martini glasses, but you can use any small serving vessel, or even small lettuce cups."
    },
    {
      "order": 5,
      "instruction": "Top with prawns. Serve, garnished with lemon wedges and a sprinkle of parsley, if using."
    }
